examples.translation: I haven’t chosen my school yet.

glosses: to be choosy about, be particular about

etymology:
From Ottoman Turkish سچمك (seçmek, “to choose, sort, discern, distinguish, notice, elect”), from Proto-Turkic *seč- (“to choose, select”).
Cognate with Old Turkic [script needed] (seç-, “to choose, discern”), Azerbaijani seçmək (“to choose, distinguish”), Turkmen seçmek (“to choose”).
